<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101224892332842></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101224892332842><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=6&mid=101224892332842>2-handed weaps or Bash?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=6&mid=101224892332842#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=121735><span id= >zegophon</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
