	   <tr><td colspan=2>The music in EQ sucks in general and a cheap sound card or onboard sound will only make it worse.&nbsp;&nbsp;Midi has this annoying habit of sustainting certain tones until something else kills them.  For me, I have to move, then the music goes back on its way.  Some of you have probably noticed this.  When you're on the boat the music will lock on a certain tone.  It's really annoying.<br><br>As of patch #9756035-4286b (^-^) my music is just broken from start to finish.  It currently now *never* plays correctly, nevermind the sustain problem.  I have turned it very low just so I always know what's going on.  There's nothing worse than standing there getting whacked and then finally realizing you turned off autoattack by accident at some point during the fight.  <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
